  meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
  meta(http-equiv='x-ua-compatible', content='ie=edge')
  //-pug syntax for including the value of a variable in the template. In this case, we are dynaically setting the title for the web page by passing data from the route.
